Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:09.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:20.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:38.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:46.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:53.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:59.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:06.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:13.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:20.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:28.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know they say,\N"there's no place like home"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but you're all so comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like some\Nstill have a way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:09.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, the young lady with\Nthe charming new hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Roatreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, this bed seems\Nto be a little lopsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not just your imagination, milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's old.\NYou can put up with that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it really bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:44.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,It creaks if I move\Njust a little, and that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't thank me\Nfor something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:22.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NSomething to do with that haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have we reached our destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:09.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,United Front
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man, what a piece of junk.\NWhere's the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:27.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the priestesses' ship?\NI imagined something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like a secret garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen one.\NHey, you! Quit socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:43.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Quit socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,This ship has Simoun\Nsibyllae on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:56.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We know. That's why we\Nwent out of our way to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of your way?\NPerfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:01.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you take me to the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't allow\Nsuch disrespect! We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you please... Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun.\NJust a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will show them the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:14.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait here, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:27.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:33.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Messis. First of all,\Nplease make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:37.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain.\NBut is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:43.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The youngsters on board this ship\Njust don't look like they're up to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:49.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,If battles could be won on the basis\Nof looks alone, I would abide by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:54.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the Simoun sibyllae\Nare the mainstay of our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is an undeniable fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:06:00.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,All sides are watching as we\Nlaunch this historical campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:03.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,There will be no room for failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,First and foremost, I believe it is\Nimportant that we trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we've agreed\Nto go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NWe're counting on you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:18.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Explain, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:26.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're about to form\Na united front with these soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,A united front?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:46.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems we'll be joining\Nforces with those men somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,With those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're being dragged\Ndown further and further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What'll become of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:08.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, a cramped ship getting\Nmore cramped is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:12.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Some people seem\Nto be enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, for real?\NYou're from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I enlisted as\Nsoon as this war began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good for you. You're an ally of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then as a reward,\NI'll show you around this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh, you see...\NI shouldn't be touching a sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:40.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't gone to the Spring yet,\Nbut that's the only difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry... I'm going\Nto become a woman anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,T-That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:52.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances,\Na lowly enlisted man like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't dare speak to a priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:59.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you not\Nto make things so complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:00.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The last few weeks,\Nenemy attacks have increased...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:11.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,...leaving us no choice but\Nto fall back from our defense lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:16.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,To keep the enemy from gaining more\Nground, we'll launch an operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:20.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to reclaim this town here,\NUrvel, their apparent target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'll go down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,First, we'll transport our troops\Nby using the Simoun planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Transport? Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:35.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll outfit the Simouns with\Nspecial transport armor to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns will transport soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:42.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,If there were another way, we'd do it.\NCan you try to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:53.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,The soldiers aboard will be deployed\Nto secret posts around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,After which the main battalion\Nwill push forward on my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll launch a pincer attack\Nand destroy the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:07.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What else do you wish us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:12.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us. Once you've\Ntransported us, your job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:18.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The operation will start the night\Nof the new moon, tomorrow at 2300.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:22.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're all\Nin top form for this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:29.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could they do such\Na thing to the Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:34.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this to our divine\Naircraft because I want to either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way! Don't you feel\Nbad for the Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:42.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, it's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,The other day,\Nwe were flying over the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:58.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we saw this huge fish, and I\Nthought, "That looks pretty tasty."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can tell she couldn't\Ncare less about the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way she's just about\Nthrowing herself at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we might not be that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:14.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,When your back's to the wall, there's\Nno time to think of others' feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,In an ideal world, we'd all\Nlearn to understand each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...just like those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can see I've been mistaken\Nabout sibyllae all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:43.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:49.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I thought sibyllae were holier,\Nthose whom must never be violated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you disillusioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you disillusioned?\NNo, totally the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm talking to you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm glad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hear you're friendly with a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, his name is Mastiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep your standing in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:27.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses\Nserving Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Indiscretions should be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That kind of talk's\Nso behind the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, I said you\Nshouldn't say things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll all go to\Nthe Spring sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then sibylla or soldier won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'll just quit being a sibylla then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then it won't be a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's fine. Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, Mastiff! You're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to get close?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:52.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Floe, you and\Nthe others serve Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and are closest to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess. Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,We too harbor\Ndeep religious convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,But rather than out of love\Nand respect for Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:07.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's because we couldn't\Ngo on if we didn't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you think of\Nthis war we're fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't like it. But we've\Ngot to fight or we'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about killing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then why did you enlist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:39.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't really explain it,\Nbut everyone else enlisted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:45.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's operation is a campaign\Nto reclaim the city where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mornings are very beautiful in Urvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:58.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Especially the view from the top of\Nthe tower in the center of the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's beyond compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, Mastiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Begin the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:51.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, men!\NBy the grace of Tempus Spatium!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:21.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll fly as close to the ground as\Npossible. Stay out of enemy sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are banning Ri Majons till further\Nnotice to avoid damaging facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:32.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,After transport, disengage\Ncontainers and retreat northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun sibyllae,\Nwe pray for your safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to say they've become ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get rid of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard not to drop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:08.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I just hope Mastiff\Ndoesn't run into any danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:13.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon,\Nthat hairstyle of yours is so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll see more of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:22.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, this is a pivotal operation,\Na springboard for future missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll understand soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is a front-line mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're almost at\Nthe drop-off point, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty quick operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll undock the containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:31.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you didn't like those things either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:36.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess. It's asking too much to even\Npretend to like such awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flares. Have they spotted us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:48.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, from the number, we should\Nassume it was a trap from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:52.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not good. If so, then those\Nold guys will get ambushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll go support them.\NUnderstood, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,They set us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, retreat!\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, they may be ugly,\Nbut they can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll keep up support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:52.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,See that? We've got\Nholy priestesses on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Step it up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right, Rimone... Keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Fire, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mastiff... Where's Mastiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, Alty, try to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaim? Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:42.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,But, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can see...\NI can see people down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:52.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pull it together. Don't dare bring any\Nmore dishonor to the priestesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:04.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, at this rate, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:06.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Ri Majon. Strike with a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know. But a Ri Majon\Nwould unleash too much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will you stand by and\Nlet those men die, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Majon ban is lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, the Iron Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:38.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't! If we do,\Nit'll put Mastiff in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,His city will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don't, he'll die anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a Ri Majon's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:58.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amazing... It's like ten tanks at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:01.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can make it...\NWe can make it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Target is city plaza,\Nthe enemy command center!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Iron Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to protect Mastiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,To protect Mastiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:33.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,They blew up\Nthe enemy command center!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:43.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could they really be\NTempus Spatium sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could that be Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right! The priestesses\Nhave cleared the way for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's show what we're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:00.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,This battle... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can't be divine aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:06.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mastiff, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:18.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't let children like that\Ntake part in a war anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:21.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,This war is ours to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:47.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:51.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:58.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:06.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:19.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:24.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:28.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:32.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:38.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:43.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:47.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:53.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:59.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:06.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:07.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NKaim and Alty have taken off on\Na reconnaissance mission as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:11.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim and Alty have taken off on\Na reconnaissance mission as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:17.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sisters\NSisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:20.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sisters
